"caption-attachment-3749880" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3749880" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dua-lipa-brits-2024.jpg" alt="Dua Lipa 全英 2024 年" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dua-lipa-brits-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dua-lipa-brits-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dua-lipa-brits-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dua-lipa-brits-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dua-lipa-brits-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dua-lipa-brits-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3749880" class="wp-caption-text">格拉斯顿伯里 2024 年头条人物杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 在全英音乐节上表演 图片来源：Gareth Cattermole/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><h2> <strong>2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的具体时间何时公布？</strong></h2><p> 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的完整阵容和演出时间将在音乐节前几周发布。自从该节日从大流行强制中断恢复以来的两年里，这些信息都是在五月的最后几天或六月的第一天发布的。</p><p>以下是迄今为止已公布的 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的阵容和舞台分布。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4fLcwiNTQ7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; wid